9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Kill | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"When an army commando finds out his true love is engaged against her will, he boards a New Dehli-bound train in a daring quest to derail the arranged marriage. But when a gang of knife-wielding thieves begin to terrorize innocent passengers on his train, the commando takes them on, one by one."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/105289/kill"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Kill"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"When an army commando finds out his true love is engaged against her will, he boards a New Dehli-bound train in a daring quest to derail the arranged marriage. But when a gang of knife-wielding thieves begin to terrorize innocent passengers on his train, the commando takes them on, one by one."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/105289/kill"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m2zXTuNPkywdYLyWlVyJZW2QOJH.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Kill"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"When an army commando finds out his true love is engaged against her will, he boards a New Dehli-bound train in a daring quest to derail the arranged marriage. But when a gang of knife-wielding thieves begin to terrorize innocent passengers on his train, the commando takes them on, one by one."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m2zXTuNPkywdYLyWlVyJZW2QOJH.jpg"}],["